 "data": "@startuml
title PLAN-IT — SystemDesign Diagram

' ===== WHITEBOARD STYLE =====
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName \"Arial\"
skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam shadowing false

skinparam rectangle {
 BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
 BorderColor #AAAAAA
 RoundCorner 15
}

skinparam package {
 BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
 BorderColor #CCCCCC
 RoundCorner 15
}

skinparam component {
 BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
 BorderColor #999999
 RoundCorner 12
}

skinparam note {
 BackgroundColor #FFF8C6
 BorderColor #E0D890
 FontColor #333333
}

skinparam ArrowColor #444444
skinparam ArrowThickness 0.8


actor User as UserIcon

' ============================================================
' FRONTEND (Based on PDF Section 2)
' ============================================================
package \"Frontend (Next.js + React)\" as FE {
 component \"Login / Register\" as LoginUI
 component \"Dashboard\" as DashboardUI
 component \"Tasks UI\" as TasksUI
 component \"Pomodoro UI\" as PomodoroUI
 component \"Analytics UI\" as AnalyticsUI
 component \"Chatbot UI\" as ChatbotUI
}

UserIcon --> LoginUI : uses browser
UserIcon --> DashboardUI
UserIcon --> TasksUI
UserIcon --> PomodoroUI
UserIcon --> AnalyticsUI
UserIcon --> ChatbotUI


' ============================================================
' BACKEND API (Based on API list in PDF Section 4)
' ============================================================
package \"Backend (Next.js API Routes)\" as BE {

 package \"Authentication APIs\" {
 component \"POST /api/auth/register\" as APIRegister
 component \"POST /api/auth/login\" as APILogin
 }

 package \"Task APIs\" {
 component \"GET /api/tasks\" as APIGetTasks
 component \"POST /api/tasks\" as APICreateTask
 component \"PUT /api/tasks/[id]\" as APIUpdateTask
 component \"DELETE /api/tasks/[id]\" as APIDeleteTask
 }

 package \"Settings APIs\" {
 component \"GET /api/settings\" as APIGetSettings
 component \"PUT /api/settings\" as APIUpdateSettings
 }

 package \"Analytics APIs\" {
 component \"GET /api/analytics/activity\" as APIAnalytics
 }

 package \"Chatbot APIs\" {
 component \"POST /api/chatbot/message\" as APIChatMessage
 }

 package \"Points APIs\" {
 component \"GET /api/points\" as APIGetPoints
 }
}


' Frontend → Backend API connections
LoginUI --> APIRegister
LoginUI --> APILogin

TasksUI --> APIGetTasks
TasksUI --> APICreateTask
TasksUI --> APIUpdateTask
TasksUI --> APIDeleteTask

DashboardUI --> APIAnalytics
AnalyticsUI --> APIAnalytics

ChatbotUI --> APIChatMessage

DashboardUI --> APIGetPoints
SettingsUI --> APIGetSettings
SettingsUI --> APIUpdateSettings


' ============================================================
' DATABASE LAYER (Based on PDF Section 3)
' ============================================================
package \"Database & External Services\n(MongoDB + OAuth + Gemini)\" as DB {

 component \"Users Collection\n(email, password, points, settings)\" as UsersModel
 component \"Tasks Collection\n(title, priority, status, dueDate)\" as TasksModel
 component \"ChatThreads\n(userId, messages, title)\" as ChatThreadsModel
 component \"TaskCompletionHistory\n(taskId, completedAt)\" as TaskHistoryModel
 component \"PointActivity\n(type, amount, description)\" as PointActivityModel

 component \"Google OAuth\" as GoogleOAuth
 component \"Gemini AI API\" as GeminiAI
}

' Backend → DB relations
APILogin --> UsersModel
APIRegister --> UsersModel
APIGetTasks --> TasksModel
APICreateTask --> TasksModel
APIUpdateTask --> TasksModel
APIDeleteTask --> TasksModel

APIChatMessage --> ChatThreadsModel
APIAnalytics --> TaskHistoryModel
APIGetPoints --> PointActivityModel
APIUpdateSettings --> UsersModel

' External services
APILogin --> GoogleOAuth : OAuth login
APIChatMessage --> GeminiAI : send prompt
GeminiAI --> APIChatMessage : AI response


' ============================================================
' SECURITY (Based on PDF Section 6)
' ============================================================
package \"Security Layer\" as SEC {
 component \"JWT Sessions\" as JWT
 component \"bcrypt Password Hashing\" as Bcrypt
 component \"Protected API Middleware\" as APIMW
 component \"Environment Secrets\" as ENV
}

APILogin --> Bcrypt
APIRegister --> Bcrypt
BE --> JWT
BE --> APIMW
BE --> ENV

@enduml
